Now, I'll dive into the resolutions, focusing on "Phường Phương Sài." I immediately spot resolution "1667/NQ-UBTVQH15," which seems promising. Bingo! That's a direct link! "Phường Phương Sài" is explicitly merged into "phường Tây Nha Trang." To be extra sure, I'll cross-reference this with the list of New Wards. I'm looking for "Phường Tây Nha Trang" in the list. Excellent, it's there: `{"ward_code":"22390","ward_name":"Phường Tây Nha Trang","province_name":"Tỉnh Khánh Hòa"}`.

This is a clear-cut case. The resolution is explicit, and the new ward is confirmed. I have high confidence in this determination.
